{"tid":1721153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣串燒保老闆娘偷相扮患癌騙20萬腫瘤科醫生推斷痔瘡致屙血","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:09:58.000Z","uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"838c1d81b35a8ca18f1e0793713cf23027298c63","tid":1721153,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"荃灣「全新串燒保」老闆娘Eva Fan（范美儀）於9月中接受我們訪問，當時指因支持反送中運動學生，而被不同政見人士恐嚇，且透露自己患有淋巴癌二期。到10月份，老闆娘在Facebook指其病情惡化，癌細胞擴散；而至11月份，由光榮冰室發起，荃灣及其他地區共12間小店為她眾籌標靶藥費，結果籌得逾20萬。<br />\n<br />\n事件在網上有很大迴響，不少人覺得在這場與極權的抗戰之中，難得體現到人間有情；然而事情峰迴路轉，於上周五（11月8日）在連登討論區，有網民證實，老闆娘9月放上Facebook，指自己在醫院治療癌症的照片，為從網上盜取使用，網民質疑之聲不絕，抨擊老闆娘使用假相及質疑她患癌的真確性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191114&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60267688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191114%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60267688&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6wexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=6ddeca34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191114%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D60267688&h=02d4a226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191114&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=60267688</a>"},{"pid":"ab792b49f154a25f03c5b2c0933def3eac41a4dd","tid":1721153,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1aa3e94bfe5bf34091c6d992d0e305aa620d69d0","tid":1721153,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"人血？"},{"pid":"1349a19ba346782100cbb8741be1c3320445e097","tid":1721153,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"838c1d81b35a8ca18f1e0793713cf23027298c63","tid":1721153,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re